'''LoginRadius Inc.''' is a cloud based SaaS [[Customer Identity Access Management]] platform based in [[Vancouver]], British Columbia, Canada.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/identity-specialist-tech-provider-loginradius-gets-17-million-series-a-1532547549|title=Identity Specialist Tech Provider LoginRadius Gets $17 Million Series A|date=2018-07-25|work=Wall Street Journal|access-date=2019-07-04|language=en-US|issn=0099-9660}}</ref> It was established in 2012.

==History==
LoginRadius was started in 2012 by two friends Deepak Gupta and Rakesh Soni as a social login widget.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.techcircle.in/2018/08/14/india-will-have-50-bn-digital-identities-in-5-years-loginradius-ceo-rakesh-soni|title=India will have 50 bn digital identities in 5 years: LoginRadius CEO Rakesh Soni|date=2018-08-14|website=Techcircle|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-04}}</ref> In an interview, Soni said the duo started the company after recognizing the hassles of registration on websites and their negative effects of conversion rates.<ref>{{cite web|title=Startup of the Week â€“ LoginRadius|url=http://calgaryherald.com/technology/startup-of-the-week-loginradius|website=Calgary Herald}}</ref>

==Platform==
According to the company, the LoginRadius platform has 200 pre-built integrations<ref>{{Cite press release|url=https://www.livemint.com/technology/tech-news/startups-that-make-travel-safe-fun-for-women-help-manage-client-identities-1560084234256.html|title=Startups that make travel safe, fun for women, help manage client identities|last=Mathur|first=Nandita|date=2019-06-09|website=LiveMint|language=en|access-date=2019-07-06}}</ref> for different customer relationship management, ad platform, and email marketing tools.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.loginradius.com/integrations/|title=LoginRadius CIAM for 3rd-Party Integrations|website=LoginRadius|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-04}}</ref> The platform is involved in the collection of customer data through traditional email based registration and through social profile data. Acquired customer data is secured in a cloud based storage. LoginRadius also provides a [[Single Customer View]] with customer data aggregated to one record. Organizations using the LoginRadius platform can integrate it with marketing tools.{{cn|date=July 2019}}

